              NOTE:

 Hesitation Marks is the upcoming eighth studio album by American industrial rock act Nine Inch Nails, to be released on September 3, 2013.
 It will be their first album since 2008's The Slip, and first release on Columbia Records, making this their first album released on a major label since 2007's Year Zero.
 The album title is derived from hesitation wounds, wounds produced by testing a bladed weapon before attempting suicide or self-harming.
